title: Olivella spretoides
text: Olivella spretoides is a <a href="species">species</a> of small <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, marine <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Olivellidae">Olivellidae</a>, the dwarf olives.
